        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 30 of the MONEY program. The session targets the time-for-money exchange as a total system: the belief that income and hours are the same thing, and that one stops when the other does.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
